<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">For fun mostly, and as a way to feed yourself.  As a Warrior, I can not forage, and money is always scarce since I have no buffs to sell.  by buying bait, I can spend a few minutes each time I log on fishing and that provides me with all my food.  I also have heard that you can now make lures and ties that eliminate the need for bait, but I have not tried that yet.  My fishing is at 131!!<p>

Jaramena Tankette<br>
